Randy,

Attached is the revised reseller agreement redline as of 3PM EST today. As you can see, there are just
a handful of outstanding items. 1) This week we completed certifications to support Discover and
Amex OptBlue on your platform. There is some new text at the top that addresses certifications to
support card brands. 2) We reduced the ongoing support fee from $50k per month to $25k as this
more accurately reflects the responsibilities, commitments and value-add. This should also remove
any concerns from either party of "showing our cards" during the diligence process as mentioned
previously. 3) We also replaced some "shall's" with "may's" in terms of new products and services.

As | am sure you guys are working in overdrive to eliminate all distractions at the Card Connect
level before "The Project" kicks off, please know we aim to do the same. Please advise if anything
else is needed on our end.

Best Regards,

Jered Isaacman | Founder & CEO
